00:01:49.050 --> 00:01:53.140
well researched and
designed non-fiction,

00:01:53.140 --> 00:01:59.580
and now the masterpiece biography
of E.B. White written for pre-teens

00:01:59.580 --> 00:02:03.750
but I'm 66 years old and think
this wonderful book will appeal

00:02:03.750 --> 00:02:06.620
