Carol that's good enough for me.

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:32.870
So my studio is part library,
part kindergarten classroom.

00:06:32.870 --> 00:06:35.720
I have everything I need
to work there all day long

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:38.470
