more than four hours.

00:06:38.470 --> 00:06:40.080
My materials are very simple.

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:43.030
I don't do any of my
art on computer.

00:06:43.030 --> 00:06:48.310
It's all by hand and it's typical
watercolor gwash [phonetic]

00:06:48.310 --> 00:06:49.910
found objects.

00:06:49.910 --> 00:06:53.600
So I'm either writing a book
or I'm illustrating a book

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:57.160 position:56%
